{"EpubVersion":2,"filepath":"","fixparentnode":"","folded":false,"markups":[{"date":"2025-03-11 21:09:16","docid":0,"id":43,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"2月28日，吴宓尚在广州，日本空袭，于是不得不前往香港，借道越南而前往云南大后方避难。","page":302,"rect":[530.5670540064513,577.9716705156188,904.1187196490109,640.3545713800535],"type":11,"uuid":"65244ae7b8a631ad5eeb6bd6495d057c"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:52:47","docid":0,"id":35,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"2月23日，吴宓购买赴越南海防之船票。","page":309,"rect":[689.1901938640501,379.23693207333974,949.0923301833494,407.58574929016714],"type":11,"uuid":"b80d5e302fa3ab0f2ec9182a34b1d19c"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:53:40","docid":0,"id":37,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"一部分香港人的势利。","page":309,"rect":[712.8925021186338,590.1267003897642,851.244339696478,609.9669966946898],"type":11,"uuid":"a909e10616640ea76a2fe7d899b5ff88"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:50:41","docid":0,"id":33,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"吴宓从叶公超处领得赴滇过安南旅行须知。","page":310,"rect":[402.93924032792347,1280.5323972412289,719.3622655619993,1305.8424569895199],"type":11,"uuid":"1809e64a5b5b9fd3af7f4cb58b17dc70"},{"date":"2025-03-11 21:06:03","docid":0,"id":39,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"吴宓兑换越币，为赴越做准备。","page":311,"rect":[491.67095840918563,241.2773430017883,698.0909632822446,279.9579356116393],"type":11,"uuid":"840f90df7dc406c28fc09da31cee2823"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:10:57","docid":0,"id":3,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"1938年3月1日下午4点，吴宓与陈梦家、赵蒙蕤夫妇及弟赵景伦、范崇武等人从香港坐船到越南。吴宓等人所乘为三等座，船上非常污秽，极为肮脏。","page":313,"rect":[125.1968077036987,1587.446901563403,797.1544567565305,1645.5755419718867],"type":11,"uuid":"0807d8e5bbdabbf9885e2aa3460ed683"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:14:59","docid":0,"id":5,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"在船上，即使二等舱，也比较颠簸。","page":314,"rect":[703.7762297130247,540.898829399475,882.239665875549,575.9329130470824],"type":11,"uuid":"3167df60e81f53868947d0e2fc383f28"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:15:59","docid":0,"id":7,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"1938年3月3日，吴宓所乘之船在自香港出发后经过琼州海峡，终于靠近安南海口。上午9点达到海防。","page":314,"rect":[436.3655724818237,876.377653925891,724.8320290053648,938.1528032966183],"type":11,"uuid":"2b7edf20b13b2c9d748e8e40103eaad2"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:17:34","docid":0,"id":9,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"中国外交人员在码头边亲自迎接吴宓一行，可知知识分子在当时所受到的礼遇。","page":314,"rect":[763.9436275900449,894.6101987371092,942.4070637525691,944.8380697273984],"type":11,"uuid":"596059ef50901be04488a1fac59b2126"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:23:00","docid":0,"id":11,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"海防天然大旅店值得注意。","page":314,"rect":[1027.1000243652952,1093.3449371793881,1094.9526886730953,1155.7278380438229],"type":11,"uuid":"baffaa974d692d7a85f58d053f694a2a"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:24:00","docid":0,"id":13,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"知识分子身上非常丑陋的一面。","page":314,"rect":[17.62479331751098,1219.7572478705013,118.29603828550411,1281.5323972412289],"type":11,"uuid":"1c10578776239414a09c160f2719e626"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:27:01","docid":0,"id":15,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"海防之建筑","page":315,"rect":[632.6693049492735,165.91615778208615,704.1684782193174,185.75645408701166],"type":11,"uuid":"4a75503e604a63ce8c25c0467684e9bf"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:27:49","docid":0,"id":17,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"越南人的经济状况、语言和社会习俗。","page":315,"rect":[1005.2209705918332,241.27734300178827,1070.0348774310971,337.0865760201232],"type":11,"uuid":"aa409221c7c6a7772c201fbc643c44c8"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:29:03","docid":0,"id":19,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"吴宓认为瘴气即硫磺气。","page":315,"rect":[991.8504377302731,473.4384135979674,1074.2891378870481,545.5453383617187],"type":11,"uuid":"d305ec480a0078d8b53ecc11bd26bc3e"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:30:16","docid":0,"id":21,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"吴宓在当地的饮食情况：咖啡牛乳和冰水。","page":315,"rect":[663.6646311283446,577.3639190219114,842.1280672908689,612.3980026695189],"type":11,"uuid":"fd3a4fd6c5fb9dd1f2a04e5660a15e29"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:31:20","docid":0,"id":24,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"吴宓等人在逃难途中依然过着非常精致的生活，这从一个侧面反映出抗战初期知识分子的生活依然相对优渥。","page":315,"rect":[7.293017924487302,636.9235654052245,102.49449944911495,755.8273551844358],"type":11,"uuid":"f2b7bc31cbba9f7ef105d4175c82a4cb"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:35:15","docid":0,"id":25,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"3月5日，吴宓一行乘滇越火车自海防前往昆明，7点开行。","page":316,"rect":[415.09427020206897,475.2616680790892,593.5577063645933,510.2957517266966],"type":11,"uuid":"3e9a8db4abdfa202d7fccd0f695173ca"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:36:03","docid":0,"id":27,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"吴宓在日记中的记载非常真实。","page":316,"rect":[18.84029630492553,751.1808462221921,87.90846360014035,843.9513217719907],"type":11,"uuid":"0cdcb9f8fed7e104fb20813933ff8772"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:37:55","docid":0,"id":29,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"天然旅店在海防和老街均有分店。","page":316,"rect":[488.6322009406493,847.813333721649,786.8226813635068,873.12339346994],"type":11,"uuid":"d8ed52fa104560cdcce6290a339cd0b8"},{"date":"2025-03-11 20:39:55","docid":0,"id":31,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linewidth":10,"originaltext":"大概3月6日7点，吴宓一行进入中国境内。吴宓一行在越南境内非常短暂，约6天。受限于此，吴宓在越南期间主要是与中国知识分子互动，与当地民众没有交流。但是，吴宓依然在其日记中记载了自己对于越南风土民情的观察。一是海防当地的建筑物，二是当地的经济状况、语言和社会风俗。同时，吴宓对于当地的饮食也多有品尝。吴宓越南游记的特点是非常真实，记载了一些高度隐私的观察和体验，但受限于时间、语言等因素而未能有所深入考察。可以说，吴宓的越南之行，基本上是走马观花。天然大旅店为一需要注意的细节。","page":317,"rect":[383.4911925292907,187.79521155554804,949.7000816770565,283.604444573883],"type":11,"uuid":"ab15c99d70078378cf7a6bea18c47830"}],"maxid":43,"notelinks":[],"title":"吴宓日记 6 1936--1938 (吴宓) (Z-Library)","unimportant":[{"date":"2025-03-11 20:10:31","docid":0,"group":[{"date":"2025-03-11 20:10:32","docid":0,"id":2,"linecolor":"ffff0000","linestyle":1,"linewidth":3,"page"